      <byline class="print_byline">By Stuart Elliott</byline>
      <abstract>
        <p>ABC Interactive, Audit Bureau of Circulations unit, names Bruce Smith to new post of president and chief executive (S)</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>Bruce Smith was named to the new post of president and chief executive at ABC Interactive, Schaumburg, Ill., the interactive auditing unit of the Audit Bureau of Circulations. He had been general manager at ChicagoSports.com, Chicago, part of the Tribune Co.</p>
      </block>
